    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Menu\nThank you for choosing Hawaiian Airlines.\nWe are pleased to offer you a unique dining experience\nwith the following selections chosen by\nChef Beverly Gannon of Hali'imaile General Store\nand Joe's in Wailea on Maui. Please choose\nthree tasting plates from the following selections:\nCheese Plate with Crackers\nThai Beef Kebob over Garlic Mashed Potatoes\nSweet and Sour Pork with Vegetable Fried Rice\nHaricot Verts, Beets, Oranges, Walnuts, Goat Cheese Salad\nCoconut Shrimp with Pineapple Salsa\nFor Dessert\nA Sweet Treat\nE'ai kakou\nHNL-SYD(1) (08/08)",
      "Menu\nHAWAIIAN\n- AIRLINES."
